#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Value-gated workflow helper for goal-spec.

The helper intentionally uses only the Python standard library. It creates and
checks local `.goal-spec` artifacts before an OpenSpec package is written, so
agents have a machine-checkable pre-spec gate instead of relying only on prompt
discipline.
"""

